Luuna: But we can't just let Lucia's tyranny continue any

Dalieh: Oh boy, if the village chief father heard about

Cain: Big brother, keep it a secret from father, okay? We'll

Luuna: At a time like this...

Dalieh: You see, I want to make you my girlfriend, Luuna. My

Cain: Geez... It's laughable that a playboy like big brother

want to make Luuna one of your sex friends, right?

Cain: Big brother's love arrows don't work on Luuna, that's
why you're interested in her, right? Most girls listen to us

Dalieh: That's right. Luuna has her childhood friend Noah
after all. Luuna, if you become my girlfriend instead of

Luuna: Dalieh, I'm sorry. To be honest Taro, you're not my

Noah: Dalieh, stop it! You're troubling Luuna.

Dalieh: Noah, it's cheeky for someone who's just a childhood

Noah: No, I've been wanting to tell Dalieh directly for a

Noah: Dalieh, let me be clear. Both Luuna and I dislike

Dalieh: Sigh... It's pitiful for Luuna to be with a poor man
with no experience with women like you.

Dalieh: Noah, just watch? I'll definitely make Luuna my

Noah: Too bad for you. Luuna dislikes flashy guys who make

Dalieh: Hmph... Luuna, you'll understand soon enough. Who
between Noah and me... is the superior male?

Becky: Sigh... Dalieh is the same as always. He messes with
any cute girl he sees. I'm glad I got married to Pole early

Pole: Heheh, I'm a lucky man to have a cute woman like Becky
as my wife. Right, Becky? You love me, don't you?

Becky: Pole, don't say embarrassing things in front of
others.

Becky: Anyway, we're going to launch a surprise attack on
the fortress in the imperial capital Jupiter-no and defeat
Lucia. We can't stand Lucia's tyranny any longer. Keep what
happens from now on a secret from the village chief.
Cain: Got it. Well, do your best out there.

Luuna: Don't worry. If it gets dangerous, we'll escape. Well
then... I'm off now.

Luuna and the resistance head towards the fortress in the
Kingdom of Jupiter-no. There, Princess Lucia and the
generals from the allied Kingdom of Valentia had gathered.
